data.description: A nice 3 bedroom ranch home with fresh interior paint, beautiful hardwood floors and a 2 car oversized garage. The family room is spacious and the kitchen is open with eat in dining. Move in ready with many big ticket items recently replaced such as roof, gutters, HVAC, windows, updated electrical panel and new sewer lines to name a few. The lower level is unfinished providing a lot of storage and yet if you need extra room it's a blank canvas you can work with. The back yard is set up for outdoor entertaining with its large deck great for family's BBQ's or circle around the firepit to roast some marshmallows.  The wood privacy fence will be enjoyed especially if you have pets and if you like to garden, you will find two nice raised beds ready to plant things this Spring. A big plus is its within walking distance to the bus line on Blue Ridge. Enjoy this great location for shopping, restaurants and easy access to several highways. A darling home, great for a first time homebuyer or someone looking to downsize.
